能会拖累", "lou": 2305, "content_length": 27, "reply_to": 866329246, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1777431494}, {"pid": 866329645, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 75, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-29 10:58", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "我先明确说明噢  今天  就是 诱多<br/>反正我吃完他诱多的诱  你们负责多", "lou": 2306, "content_length": 56, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1777431539}, {"pid": 866330226, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 21, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-29 11:02", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=866330016,45974302,4497]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=43098419]勇敢的天线宝宝[/uid] (2026-04-29 11:01):[/b]<br/><br/>稀土也是吗[/quote]<br/>长线的不是 <br/>我今天开的游戏 军工船都不是  这些都是稳定过51的", "lou": 2307, "content_length": 59, "reply_to": 866330016, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1777431756}, {"pid": 866330386, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 22, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-29 11:03", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=866330117,45974302,4497]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=60336410]小丸子不在家[/uid] (2026-04-29 11:01):[/b]<br/><br/>怎么看出来诱多的啊，因为缩量，大金融也没发力吗[/quote]<br/>打开你的APP  点开量能 告诉我  现在是不是缩转放的过程", "lou": 2308, "content_length": 52, "reply_to": 866330117, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1777431809}, {"pid": 866331975, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 67, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-29 11:12", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=866331699,45974302,4499]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=25646105]luyifan19941107[/uid] (2026-04-29 11:11):[/b]<br/><br/>那今天买药？？！[/quote]<br/>你TXXX有病啊  全面普涨反弹修复的时候你去买反向防守的。你不怕等下指数突一下4100  你手上的被摁？<br/>你就不能等指数见顶的那时候再去？", "lou": 2309, "content_length": 127, "reply_to": 866331699, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1777432378}, {"pid": 866332279, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 34, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-29 11:14", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=866332078,45974302,4499]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=40319180]SaikaDeath[/uid] (2026-04-29 11:13):[/b]<br/><br/>今天这朝气蓬勃的，前面几天都是3000+下跌，今天难得这么好看，结果居然是在诱多，XX的大A[s:ac:哭1][/quote]<br/>大哥。。你读过书吗   书上对我们怎么对抗糖衣炮弹是怎么描述的？", "lou": 2310, "content_length": 63, "reply_to": 866332078, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1777432493}, {"pid": 866332563, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 26, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-29 11:16", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=866332290,45974302,4500]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=67128788]天天困困困[/uid] (2026-04-29 11:14):[/b]<br/><br/>啊 今天是普涨吗 为啥我手上的票全是绿的[/quote]<br/>我哪里知道 你自己检讨自己。板块都不到10个是绿的", "lou": 2311, "content_length": 51, "reply_to": 866332290, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1777432594}, {"pid": 866335188, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 21, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-29 11:32", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=866334631,45974302,4502]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=38534514]晨星233[/uid] (2026-04-29 11:29):[/b]<br/><br/>狼大我发现，我们散户朋友耐心差的不行。<br/>您说诱多的时候，我觉得马上就要见顶，得赶紧跑。然后马上跑去做反指。[/quote]<br/><br/>我说要卖了？", "lou": 2312, "content_length": 17, "from_client": "8 Android", "reply_to": 866334631, "postdatetimestamp": 1777433571}, {"pid": 866335318, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 50, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-29 11:33", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=866335148,45974302,4502]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=67177418]小蝎子ICE二代[/uid] (2026-04-29 11:32):[/b]<br/><br/>鹏辉，中一堪称光明左右使<br/>里面主力是不是有仓位控制强迫症，卖了一个就要去拉另一个<br/>自从狼大说锂电不要加了之后没管过，目送了[/quote]<br/><br/>你有没有考虑过主力可能是同一批人 他是不是要卖了这个有钱才能做下一个？<br/>当然我先说 和我无关系啊", "lou": 2313, "content_length": 95, "from_client": "8 Android", "reply_to": 866335148, "postdatetimestamp": 1777433626}, {"pid": 866351671, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 72, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-29 13:43", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "不会有人这个位置追进去吧？有的话麻烦出这个门左转圆润的弹开", "lou": 2314, "content_length": 58, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1777441417}, {"pid": 866352037, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 52, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-29 13:46", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "这里持仓等卖点就行了  截至目前不是卖点。<br/>但是如果这个时候追进去，不管你今天挣多少  很快就能亏出去。这是操作体系的问题。", "lou": 2315, "content_length": 114, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1777441584}, {"pid": 866352141, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 47, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-29 13:47", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=866351921,45974302,4514]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=295108]jimddr[/uid] (2026-04-29 13:45):[/b]<br/><br/>难道说，昨天才是最佳进场点？[/quote]<br/>今早才是进场点，你怎么总是后视镜看  <br/>看见能进的迹象才是进场点  而不是 已经涨起来了 去懊悔昨天为什么不进  因为昨天就没有能进场的迹象。", "lou": 2316, "content_length": 129, "reply_to": 866351921, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1777441643}, {"pid": 866352423, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 34, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-29 13:49", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=866352246,45974302,4515]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=60702981]Coldcarina[/uid] (2026-04-29 13:48):[/b]<br/><br/>军工船和游戏也是吗[/quote]<br/>无FXXK可说", "lou": 2317, "content_length": 15, "reply_to": 866352246, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1777441790}, {"pid": 866352714, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 33, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-29 13:52", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][